{"tid":923437,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《Uncharted》系列電影準備開拍！Tom Holland確定演出Nathan Drake！","createTime":"2018-12-01T09:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T10:29:07.000Z","uid":212399,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d560dc25c5d7a4f913fb78f2ba3bbb628639e244","tid":923437,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T09:01:10.000Z","msg":"著名遊戲製作室Naughty dog名作《Uncharted》系列要電影化的消息早就不絕於耳，作品的電影化也一向很受期待，(之前甚至還出現了製作精美的FansMade短片！)而實際上遠從2009年開始就有電影化的相關消息，但到了最近，總算是塵埃落定，因為導演 Shawn Levy 已經公布一切已準備就緒，電影馬上就要開拍了。<br />\n正如之前放出的消息一般，主角Nathan Drake一角將預定會由年輕演員Tom Holland，即在目前最新版Spiderman中飾演主角蜘蛛俠的演員演出！<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.3igame.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/word-image-22.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3igame.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2Fword-image-22.png&h=7c6efd3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實Nathan在遊戲中的身手真的可以媲美蜘蛛俠了&hellip;<br />\n記得剛聽到這消息的時候大家其實都驚訝覺得Tom Holland外型上實在太年輕了，擔心會演不出Nathan的&rdquo;佬&rdquo;感，更有人提議Nathan這種運氣差(笑)又玩世不恭的角色交給星爵(Chris Pratt)或者外型比較接近的鷹眼(Jeremy Renner)會更好；但根據官方公布的故事概念，該電影作品並不會直接拍遊戲本篇的內容，而是從Uncharted 3中Nathan的少年回憶片段中獲得靈感製作的前傳式故事，也就是說登場的會是剛跟師父Sullivan相識的年輕版的Nathan！<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.3igame.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/word-image-23-1024x576.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3igame.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2Fword-image-23-1024x576.png&h=468d85e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n年輕版感覺幾適合<br />\n另外雖然其他演員的陣容一切都未公布，但Holland自己似乎就希望Chris Pratt能參與演出主角的老師Sullivan一角，正如前述，Chris Pratt的氣質一向都被認為擅長飾演一些玩世不恭的流氓型角色，而且其實不只網民們覺得Chris Pratt適合演出Nathan(成年版)，連Holland自己都這麼認為，<br />\n所以他也認為大盜Sullivan這樣的角色讓Chris Pratt演出一定很棒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.3igame.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/word-image-24-1024x576.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3igame.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2Fword-image-24-1024x576.png&h=661ff9a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影既然已經馬上開拍，相信大家的等待也不再遙遙無期，也許之前說的預定2020年真的能如期上映，還請大家繼續期待！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3igame.com/%e3%80%8auncharted%e3%80%8b%e7%b3%bb%e5%88%97%e9%9b%bb%e5%bd%b1%e6%ba%96%e5%82%99%e9%96%8b%e6%8b%8d%ef%bc%81tom-holland%e7%a2%ba%e5%ae%9a%e6%bc%94%e5%87%banathan-drake%ef%bc%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3igame.com%2F%25e3%2580%258auncharted%25e3%2580%258b%25e7%25b3%25bb%25e5%2588%2597%25e9%259b%25bb%25e5%25bd%25b1%25e6%25ba%2596%25e5%2582%2599%25e9%2596%258b%25e6%258b%258d%25ef%25bc%2581tom-holland%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e5%25ae%259a%25e6%25bc%2594%25e5%2587%25banathan-drake%25ef%25bc%2581&d=6QdQly7TZhMNNtULIaCvDnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=7217e5be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3igame.com/%e3%80%8auncharted%e3%80%8b%e7%b3%bb%e5%88%97%e9%9b%bb%e5%bd%b1%e6%ba%96%e5%82%99%e9%96%8b%e6%8b%8d%ef%bc%81tom-holland%e7%a2%ba%e5%ae%9a%e6%bc%94%e5%87%banathan-drake%ef%bc%81</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cosmicbooknews.com/tom-holland-wants-chris-pratt-uncharted-movie\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmicbooknews.com%2Ftom-holland-wants-chris-pratt-uncharted-movie&d=6QdQly7TZhMNNtULIaCvDnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=9e216b06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cosmicbooknews.com/tom-holland-wants-chris-pratt-uncharted-movie</a>"},{"pid":"d52dd6512155d0ad69187e21ddf138e99175081b","tid":923437,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T09:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b2e48bb9631ce5692c9df1168d7cba979f1492","tid":923437,"uid":48791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T09:25:44.000Z","msg":"真係無佬味"},{"pid":"b5ab1f36adc1fe956b88e9c9f502a1c8ecd39174","tid":923437,"uid":24024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T09:32:16.000Z","msg":"Chris Pratt+Tom Holland<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf362ab2d4c671ebaeebc2acd6a77b2f58d9e75","